data.description: Charming 3Bed/1Bath Bungalow located in a excellent neighborhood!  Large open living room and dining room concept, that leads to kitchen and a spacious sunken family room. The main level also features original hardwood floors throughout, fireplace, updated bathroom, newer furnace, and plenty of windows bringing in natural light with beautiful scenery. Upstairs there is another bedroom + a bonus space just waiting on your creativity (office, walk-in closet, bathroom?). This property sits on a oversized lot, with a a lot of parking options and a fenced backyard perfect for entertaining or relaxing! Easy walkable/bikeable commute to grocery stores, retail stores, restaurants and parks!
